name: Cyber Troopers Virtual-On Oratorio Tangram
summary: Cyber Troopers VirtualOn Oratorio Tangram is the first of three major revisions to Cyber Troopers VirtualOn Oratorio Tangram a sequel to Cyber Troopers VirtualOn MSBS Ver 52 was released for Sega Model 3 arcade hardware and is thought to have been exlusive to Japan
